Change activemq logs to your desired location

Change active_home in below file

/insalled/location/apache-activemq-5.9.1/bin/linux-x86-64/wrapper.conf
set.default.ACTIVEMQ_DATA = /set/ur/own/path


Ex:

/opt/igc_services/igc_datastore_software/apache-activemq-5.9.1/bin/linux-x86-64/wrapper.conf


set.default.ACTIVEMQ_DATA=/opt/igc_services/runtime/activemq/data

change log files in below:
===============================

to change log files directory in below file

/installed/location/apache-activemq-5.9.1/conf/log4j.properties
log4j.appender.audit.file=/set/ur/path/


/opt/igc_services/igc_datastore_software/apache-activemq-5.9.1/conf/log4j.properties

log4j.appender.audit.file=/opt/igc_services/runtime/activemq/log/audit.log




